cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/amssw/duranti/geant4.11.3.2-install -DGEANT4_USE_GDML=ON -DGEANT4_BUILD_MULTITHREADED=ON  -DGEANT4_INSTALL_DATA=ON -DGEANT4_INSTALL_DATADIR=/amssw/duranti/geant4-share -DCMAKE_CXX_STANDARD=17 -DGEANT4_USE_QT=ON -DGEANT4_USE_QT_QT6=ON -DGEANT4_USE_OPENGL_X11=ON ../geant4.11.3.2

e poi, ovviamente:

make -j8
make install
